            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". While some wondered if the COVID-19 pandemic would kill car collecting as a hobby, we saw the exact opposite happen. It turns out when you take away swanky vacations and a lot of other activities, forcing people to stay home, they turn to ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
